{"tid":267501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國熱到解放乳頭 34C歐陽巧瑩真空出巡","createTime":"2017-06-02T10:30:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-02T14:53:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"00321a77e2337dbc941473c9c72c267974b51307","tid":267501,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T10:30:01.000Z","msg":"人要唞氣，原來乳頭都要唞唞氣㗎，34C「黑色乳牛」歐陽巧瑩今日喺instagram上載咗一張真空着住吊帶牛仔褲嘅相，打ashtag「freethenipple」，原來正喺美國度假!<br />\n<br />\n身在異地嘅歐陽巧瑩，就好豪放咁真空着住吊帶牛仔褲出街，好大膽咁解放自己嘅乳頭。但原來歐陽巧瑩咁做係有意思㗎，freethenipple意思係「解放乳頭運動」，佢咁做只係響應依個運動，而運動嘅目的係追求性別平等。<br />\n<br />\n好多網民見到都睇到流晒鼻血，仲留言問佢點解喺香港唔咁樣出街，但亦有網民好有心咁提醒佢要小心走光喎！歐陽巧瑩平時都唔吝嗇咁喺社交網晒騷胸泳照，但今次咁大膽咁真空出街，唔知佢有冇問過男朋友林師傑呢！？ <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170602/large/1496382870_49ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170602%2Flarge%2F1496382870_49ed.jpg&h=1b8e1e59&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b39b6e23139ba096c86427a23c8e44162b541a9b","tid":267501,"uid":34343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T12:07:20.000Z","msg":"邊撚過黎"},{"pid":"960912cd7505ff8f7361115930c2dc2504397316","tid":267501,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T12:18:23.000Z","msg":"C都可以叫乳牛？<br />\n咁D、E嗰啲叫乜？"},{"pid":"ea468cf57f1ff09f088c3eff507586768a576289","tid":267501,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T12:18:28.000Z","msg":"工人褲大哥fans<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddd40b06d29dda937cf2fe5a426530930da9daab","tid":267501,"uid":31323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T12:37:44.000Z","msg":"1. 佢邊位？<br />\n2. 這是不對的"},{"pid":"8f7d3426b94ce1868155b42d459fb124ff844a18","tid":267501,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T12:43:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 佢邊位？<br />\n2. 這是不對的</blockquote><br />\n<